{"tid":1659290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"10月18日開始，大家正式食瀝青雞，瀝青豬，飲瀝青水","createTime":"2019-10-17T01:06:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T15:51:41.000Z","uid":318752,"like":84,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"d653945f6282fb85b4d95611024ab524dc958948","tid":1659290,"uid":318752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T01:06:56.000Z","msg":"新屋嶺有間瀝青廠係我發現，所以我有責任跟到尾。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/tpb/tc/plan_application/A_NE-FTA_192.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Ftpb%2Ftc%2Fplan_application%2FA_NE-FTA_192.html&d=o%2BN67aGUGKsADGfJqajrgH4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=4cf64cb1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/tpb/tc/plan_application/A_NE-FTA_192.html</a><br />\n<br />\n新屋嶺 瀝青化工廠 24號前 停止接受市民意見<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589376\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589376</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n【突發，超緊急】赤共已安排於新屋嶺毒殺全港市民<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1550265\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1550265</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n明天 10月18號，城規會就會審理呢單野。<br />\n<br />\n其實有少少失望，連登3千幾個正評，實際得千零個意見提交左。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gFaney7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgFaney7.jpg&h=f455a2c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過，算啦，腥港人係咁，我明，呢單野都可以完美展示港共的制度暴力。就算有再多反對意見，我地都阻止唔到任何野。<br />\n<br />\n城規會個架步係<br />\n香港北角渣華道333號<br />\n北角政府合署15樓會議室(1537室)<br />\n<br />\n下午兩點半開會<br />\n<br />\n有興趣既可以去旁聽，見証香港人正式食瀝青雞同瀝青豬同飲瀝青水既開始。<br />\n<br />\n近排病左，做左一排CD ROM 。食藥都食到個人灰灰地，打呢篇野個陣，個心真係感到好無奈。<br />\n<br />\n希望城規會明天可以被休會，唔係見到d雞肉都唔開胃。"},{"pid":"9da072fd94d302ac40056b2bb5eff490b9556f3c","tid":1659290,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T01:07:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dC4rszp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdC4rszp.jpg&h=a54a4986&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"2dc085f3575b3fc43fcf26401b933508b4bbc968","tid":1659290,"uid":318752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T01:09:02.000Z","msg":"P 牌推唔到，都唔想推，上來呻下就算。"},{"pid":"bebf8bec1528f0247f14fd3a47cf2f3b7a1de2ac","tid":1659290,"uid":69385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T01:11:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"20401de6ecfc431972aac8949057921c86e02442","tid":1659290,"uid":297334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T01:12:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DDsAzEX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDDsAzEX.jpg&h=c720194e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sbBaoyj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsbBaoyj.jpg&h=dddabbc4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A5hMGj1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA5hMGj1.jpg&h=5c90f67d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Co7HY6H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCo7HY6H.jpg&h=af8d833a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dP9LcrJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdP9LcrJ.jpg&h=c04f8e23&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5QpfzE4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5QpfzE4.jpg&h=4615a3e4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zFFB3yq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzFFB3yq.jpg&h=9ecafcf5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L5BhNZ6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL5BhNZ6.jpg&h=3646742b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xK3Tmj7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxK3Tmj7.jpg&h=1f40a36f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DMqZgTu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.l